              <p>Multi-tenant isolation — access rules verified so one company's survey data, admins, and branding can
                never leak into another's, even sharing the same backend.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tags"><span>Odoo</span><span>Multi-tenant Security</span><span>E-commerce</span></div>
          </div>
